        </div>

        <div style=" width:200px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align:center; padding: 15px">
            <img src='https://i.pinimg.com/736x/2a/32/e8/2a32e805c6605abae8f18a7677150201.jpg'
                 alt="Coffe Cup"
                 style="width: 100%; border-radius: 10px"> 
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold"> Espresso </p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px"> Medium ₱ 80.00 <br />Large ₱ 100.00 </p>
